Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是职业球探吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.10,0:02:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.70,0:02:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前来这里的人不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.90,0:02:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是被全球坛所注目的高中生黄金右碗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.50,0:02:31.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是羡慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.00,0:02:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0000FF&}被玷污的投手丘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.00,0:02:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室…室井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.00,0:03:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们俩是一个中学的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.60,0:03:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道室井家的对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.70,0:03:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我送他回家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.00,0:03:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 岩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.00,0:03:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你们应该知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.60,0:03:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们两个闹着玩从堤坝上摔下来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.00,0:03:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.90,0:03:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.70,0:03:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 岩下 我求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.00,0:03:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 他就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.50,0:03:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 岩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.60,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是没什么事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.90,0:03:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是跟老师反映一下事实真相吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了又能怎么样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.40,0:03:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情宣扬出去一下子就会被禁赛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家应该和我一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很想参加大赛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.60,0:04:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能出线之后就是全国大赛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.40,0:04:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不甘心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为了这个没有那个小子不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.20,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我一个人忍忍就没事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么会被打啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.40,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.70,0:04:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是因为越受注目也就有越多的压力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.80,0:04:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 失望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.20,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么倍受职业球坛瞩目的高中生黄金右腕嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.80,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(656,469)}好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.20,0:04:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(380,469)}哎呀哎呀 到底发生了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.30,0:04:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把他从堤坝上推下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹着玩时 一不小心就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.10,0:04:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闹过头了吧 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次当心点 知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是见到室井的最后一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.30,0:04:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室井在第二天和第三天都没有来学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后在之后的那天早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个令大家悲痛的消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.70,0:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1年C班的室井伸一不幸去世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说似乎是内脏破裂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.90,0:05:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他做了什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.20,0:05:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是被谁打了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.90,0:05:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为室井君的去世默哀一分钟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.70,0:05:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么有什么事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了啊 室井他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是这样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前辈你的错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的错吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.70,0:05:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证…证据 这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.10,0:05:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么可能有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.90,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 你倒应该担心一下自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:06:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真的假的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱通信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.50,0:06:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说午夜零点登录的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女就会帮你消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.10,0:06:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 不要再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.60,0:06:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.90,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教导主任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是刑警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.20,0:06:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于室井的死有些事想要问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.60,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你将他从堤坝上推了下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.70,0:06:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 从验尸结果看如果不用棒装物体殴打的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.10,0:06:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会造成这样的伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.10,0:06:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.50,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗 岩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是那样的话 大赛就完了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.70,0:06:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.00,0:07:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你的错 都是因为你伸一才
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.00,0:07:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸一有多痛苦你知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.40,0:07:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在临死的时候还在喊疼啊 疼啊的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在床上翻滚着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此那个孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.80,0:07:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还在说不是你的错 不是你的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.20,0:07:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.00,0:07:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.40,0:07:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把伸一还给我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.20,0:07:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 冷静点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 那是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.70,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.30,0:07:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室井 我和你约定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.00,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果成了职业选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会连你那份一起努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是花笠啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.10,0:07:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花笠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.80,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混帐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸 听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都误会我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.60,0:08:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真…真不知道说什么好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想您都无法原谅他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请您 请您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.40,0:08:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 滚回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回去 今天我们会回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.70,0:08:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我们改日再登门道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道歉可不便宜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.80,0:08:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几千万 不 还是几亿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.80,0:08:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.30,0:08:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该怎么做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.50,0:08:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 求你们了 请相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样请你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先跟我们走一趟再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住 岩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.40,0:10:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)}君之怨恨    愿为消之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.60,0:10:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个传言 是真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想去吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.70,0:10:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.60,0:10:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可奈何啊 不干不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可奈何啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.20,0:11:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次之后就连不上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候在那里的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呼唤我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是阎魔爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.10,0:11:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.50,0:11:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.00,0:11:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请收下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你若真的要消除怨恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将那红线解开即可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.10,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开绳线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.50,0:11:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就和我正式缔结了契约
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.90,0:11:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怨恨的人将立刻坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.30,0:11:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨恨若已消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.50,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自身亦将付出代价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害人终害己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,缔结契约后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.80,0:12:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亦将坠入地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.70,0:12:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是死之后的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.80,0:12:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.60,0:12:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.90,0:12:31.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.90,0:12:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的事 就由你自己抉择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.50,0:12:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大赛都无法参加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛还要练习啊 棒球部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.70,0:12:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式指示还没下来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可真是灾难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.70,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常都在想 不觉得连带责任不妥吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.70,0:13:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花笠同学 真可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花笠同学在大赛上的活跃表现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.60,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很期待的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.50,0:13:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同学 不用离这那远 过来这边吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 那个女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.20,0:13:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我来了 快出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.40,0:13:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花笠 前辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.70,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己做的事 请自己承担起责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于我来说 这过于沉重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.40,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.40,0:14:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我会说“是 我会的”吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.30,0:14:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不答应的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.00,0:14:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我也有的办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将真相申诉出来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.30,0:14:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这个你昨晚也试过了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.70,0:14:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像没有人相信你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.10,0:14:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花笠前辈对于室井的死一点想法都没有的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过觉得他很倒霉哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没想到他会死掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.40,0:14:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了 从一开始他就不适合打棒球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着 你要打我也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是等于你自己认罪了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.00,0:14:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 把我打伤了可不会简单了事哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把我投球的手弄伤可是很严重的事情哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.50,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上室井的赔偿费 你们家就要破产了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.50,0:14:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么办啊 我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么样关我屁事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.00,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要露出这种表情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.30,0:15:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我还要感谢你和室井呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.50,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏你们 可以不用参加大赛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.90,0:15:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部员们可能想要留些青春的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.10,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过为了这个就要耗损我的肩膀就有点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.90,0:15:16.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球探们似乎也建议我不要参赛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.50,0:15:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐 难道说是故意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.90,0:15:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的话 你又想怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.40,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.70,0:15:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室井他 室井他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.20,0:15:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦地 痛苦地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.90,0:15:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.30,0:15:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.50,0:15:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我又没有看见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.20,0:15:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了 没事了吧 再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.40,0:15:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是劝你早点去警察那自首比较好哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.50,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然审讯时会给法官留下种种不好的印象的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.40,0:16:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨 恨 已 闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 长衫放好了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.80,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.30,0:16:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们想把你作为今年选秀的第一指名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.00,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也愿意出大量契约的金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.20,0:17:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.00,0:17:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.80,0:17:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花笠 花笠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人凶手 杀人凶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂停
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有最后一个人出局就是完封了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.60,0:18:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 这是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道这是人的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.70,0:18:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 还有一个出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.00,0:18:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 不知道出局的意思吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.20,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你吧 就是杀了的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.70,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室井出局 岩下出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.20,0:18:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,室井出局 岩下出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.90,0:18:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花笠出局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.30,0:18:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑啊 你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.50,0:18:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打者 岩下君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.80,0:18:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你干的好事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 真是烦人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.20,0:18:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧吧 这样就到赛点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不想听什么借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.40,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为你准备的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶作剧也要适可而止啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.70,0:19:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是恶作剧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球就是事关生死的严肃比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.90,0:19:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 继续比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.90,0:19:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会让你得逞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.90,0:19:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.40,0:19:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.90,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.70,0:19:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不承认自己的罪吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.00,0:19:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.00,0:19:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了一个人 还让另一个人承担罪责不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.50,0:20:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得那两个人可怜吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.90,0:20:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会怎么样关我什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.00,0:20:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为自己会打点棒球就跟一般人不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.40,0:20:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么事情都会被原谅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自以为是也要有个限度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.90,0:20:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们都不看报纸的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不是稍微会打点的程度而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是被称为十年难得一见的奇才啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.80,0:20:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不能打棒球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.60,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本 不 对世界职业棒球来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给带来多大的影响你不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.80,0:20:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们应该知道吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岩下也好 室井也好都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.70,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了我而死应该可以瞑目了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他这么说呢 小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.50,0:20:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷失于黑暗中的可悲之影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤害鄙视他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.90,0:20:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺于罪恶的孽魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.90,0:20:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来死一次吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.80,0:21:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.10,0:21:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.30,0:21:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为想打棒球而进入棒球部的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是和花笠同学不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或许不能成为职业选手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.50,0:21:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就算玩玩业余棒球也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直想继续打棒球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.60,0:21:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过已经再也不能打棒球了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.30,0:21:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么想打 随你怎么去打不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.60,0:21:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 那么我们一起打好了 花笠同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.00,0:21:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人去打 我才不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.50,0:21:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 花笠同学你不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.40,0:21:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棒球一个人是没办法打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.50,0:21:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此怨此恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.60,0:21:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将流向地狱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.70,0:22:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.20,0:22:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说是少年A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.40,0:22:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实很明显的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说是职业界非常瞩目的棒球王牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.10,0:22:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 在报纸和电视上也常露脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.40,0:22:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目击者也说他用棒球棍殴打后辈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.60,0:22:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道那个人是花笠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.70,0:22:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他到底消失到哪里去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.00,0:22:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拜托过你伯母了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.40,0:22:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么困难就马上打电话给我们好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.20,0:22:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.00,0:22:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔的话 你是不是也能回一次家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.60,0:22:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等事情平静下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.00,0:22:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我想这需要花费一点时间吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.00,0:23:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君之怨恨 愿为消之
